data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bed, 2.5-bath residence with elegant hardwood floors, adding a touch of sophistication and practicality. The designated dining area is perfect for hosting memorable family dinners or entertaining friends, creating a focal point for shared meals and special occasions. Experience the luxury of generously sized bedrooms, providing comfort and ample space for relaxation, each designed with your comfort in mind. Work from home with ease in the office area, offering a quiet and productive space for focused tasks and virtual meetings. Enjoy the outdoors on not one, but two elevated decks! Perfect for morning coffee, evening sunsets, or hosting gatherings with a scenic view. Embrace the joys of outdoor living in the large backyard, providing endless possibilities for recreation, gardening, or simply unwinding in nature. The unfinished basement presents a canvas for your creative ideas - a potential space for a home gym, playroom, or additional living quarters, limited only by your imagination.  This home seamlessly blends classic charm with modern conveniences, offering a lifestyle that caters to both traditional and contemporary tastes. This property is not just a house; it's a haven where memories are made and cherished for a lifetime. Conveniently located near restaurants, activities, parks, and more, making it an ideal choice for those seeking both tranquility and accessibility. With all these features, this home is move-in ready, awaiting a new chapter with its lucky owners. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
